description: Welcome to 161 H Street Unit 3.  This Beautiful 2 bed, 1 bath, top floor unit is located in the coveted East Side of South Boston. Sunny and bright, hardwood floors throughout, spacious white kitchen with granite & stainless steel appliances, central ac, in-unit washer/dryer, additional basement storage, rear deck and exclusive roof deck with great water views make this an fabulous home. Situated just two blocks to the beach, and three blocks to East Broadway for easy access to restaurants, bars and shops. Easy walk to Stop & Shop, Walgreens, Post Office and other conveniences Broadway has to offer. Unit has just been painted - common hallway just painted and new carpet to be installed in next couple of weeks.  Make an appt today and don’t miss this fab unit!
